descriptionHtml:
Blackjack is a classic casino card game that's easy to learn but difficult to master. Score more points than the dealer but don't go over 21! Strategize, calculate, risk and win loads of chips. There are no losers in this casino - our dealers always make sure that you have chips left to continue playing even after an unlucky streak. So what are you waiting for? Come on in and let's play some Blackjack!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Introducing: Blackjack Duels!
Play in the most popular casinos in the world but don't do it on an empty stomach! Collect refreshments, upgrade them and receive gems.
But that's not all!
Experience the dynamic Duel mode where you bet against another player on who can win more chips from the dealer in just six turns!
Make the best possible use of the currency exchange, increase your collection, try out various refreshments and master the Duel mode!
All that (and more!) in the Blackjack Duels!
